        <span class="section-label">My Story</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Local focus, web expertise</h2>
        <p>Localweb.care was born out of a simple idea: local businesses deserve better web solutions. I saw too many small companies struggling with cookie-cutter outdated WordPress and Squarespace websites that promise everthing to everyone but end up being nothing for anyone.</p>
        <p>Run by Jim Smits, a web developer with over a decade of experience, localweb.care combines deep technical expertise with a passion for helping local businesses succeed online. </p>
        <p>I understand the unique challenges and opportunities that come with serving a local market, and we're here to provide solutions that are tailored to your specific needs.</p>
        
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="section-label">My Approach</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Thoughtful. Transparent. Effective.</h2>
        <p>Every project starts with listening. I want to understand your customers, your market, and your goals before I touch a single pixel or write a line of code.</p>
        <p>From there I build with the tools best suited to your needs — fast static sites built with an eye on performance, accessibility, and long-term maintainability.</p>
        <p>Once live, I don't disappear. Ongoing partnerships keep your site fresh, your rankings strong, and your strategy aligned with how your business grows.</p>
